import React from 'react';
import { InputGroup, Button, FormControl } from 'react-bootstrap';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';


function ConfidenceForm() {
    return (
        <>
            <Form inline>
                <Form.Label className="mb-2 mr-sm-2" htmlFor="inlineFormCustomSelect" >
                    Confidence
                </Form.Label>
                <Form.Control
                    as="select"
                    className="mb-2 mr-sm-2"
                    id="inlineFormCustomSelect"
                    custom
                >
                    <option value="0">Choose...</option>
                    <option value="90">90%</option>
                    <option value="95">95%</option>
                    <option value="99">99%</option>
                </Form.Control>
                <Form.Label className="mb-2 mr-sm-2" htmlFor="inlineFormInputName2" >
                    Start Date
                </Form.Label>
                <Form.Control
                    type="date"
                    className="mb-2 mr-sm-2"
                    id="inlineFormInputName2"
                    placeholder="Start Date"
                />
                <Form.Label className="mb-2 mr-sm-2" htmlFor="inlineFormInputName" srOnly>
                    Periods
                </Form.Label>
                <Form.Control
                    type="number"
                    min="0"
                    max=""
                    size="1000"
                    value="14"
                    className="mb-2 mr-sm-2"
                    id="inlineFormInputName" 
                    placeholder="Periods" 
                />
                <Button type="submit" className="mb-2">
                    Update
                </Button>
            </Form>
        </>
    )
}

export default ConfidenceForm
